    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to culture, style, and period of the Chinese dynasty that succeeded the Wei. The Western Jin flourished from 265 to 316 CE and the Eastern Jin from 317 to 420 CE.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
